data.description: Move in Ready! This Charming bungalow in a convenient Peoria location sitting on a large DOUBLE lot, .58 Acre, with privacy! Such a great space for outdoor entertainment. This 2 bedroom and 1 bath home has so much character and so many updates! The roof in 2010, windows, siding and kitchen appliances 2013, HVAC in 2014, water heater in 2015. Beautiful trim, arched doors, hardwood floor. With a finished basement there is plenty of space to relax! A Home Warranty available with acceptable offer. You have to see this one yourself!
